This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent complexity of climate systems, which involve numerous interacting variables. Additionally, while the sources used are reputable, the rapidly evolving nature of climate science means that new findings could alter current understandings. Further research and continuous monitoring are essential to refine these insights.

